text: Kurshalino () is a rural locality (a village) in Novomeshcherovsky Selsoviet, Mechetlinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 236 as of 2010. There are 3 streets. == Geography == It is located 37 km from Bolsheustyikinskoye, 2 km from Novomeshcherovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Mechetlinsky District
title: Kurshalino
